0.3
* Removal of Spring dependency (Thanks, Imre)
* Removal of commons-io dependency (Thanks, again, Imre)
* Moved to the BSD license
* Injection bug fixes
* Added support for Mojarra 2
* Better encapsulation of Mojarra-specific code to make supporting other impls easier
* Added support for Servlet filters
* Added suport for Servlet listeners
* Various XML parsing bug fixes
* Moved JSF (Mojarra) 2 code to a new module to resolve run-time issues with update to Mojarra 1.2_13
* Build/test changes invisible to the end user

